{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/set-typescript-webpack-babel","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"66a515ab-fc62-5ff0-8f0c-e3e606c7b971","html":"<h3 id=\"javascript-환경-설정하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#javascript-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"javascript 환경 설정하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>javascript 환경 설정하기</h3>\n<p>typescript, webpack, babel 등등</p>\n<h4 id=\"directory-structure\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#directory-structure\" aria-label=\"directory structure permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>directory structure</h4>\n<h4 id=\"tsc\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tsc\" aria-label=\"tsc permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>tsc</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">tsc --init</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"webpack-install\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#webpack-install\" aria-label=\"webpack install permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>webpack install</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add -D webpack webpack-dev-server webpack-cli\nyarn add -D html-webpack-plugin clean-webpack-plugin</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">plugins: [\n  new CleanWebpackPlugin(),\n  new HtmlWebpackPlugin({\n    template: `./public/index.html`\n  })\n]</code></pre></div>\n<p>플러그인을 통헤 템플릿을 지정하면 알아서 번들링된 js파일을 추가해준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&quot;scripts&quot;: {\n    &quot;build&quot;: &quot;webpack&quot;,\n    &quot;watch&quot;: &quot;webpack-dev-server --inline --hot&quot;\n  },</code></pre></div>\n<p>package.json에 빌드와 로컬 서버를 위한 스크립트를 추가해주었다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"babel-install\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#babel-install\" aria-label=\"babel install permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>babel install</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add -D @babel/core @babel/preset-env @babel/preset-typescript babel-loader</code></pre></div>\n<p>babel에서 ts의 문법을 변환해줄 수 있다.<br>\n간단히 webpack.confg.js 에 모듈을 추가해주었다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"webpackconfigjs\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#webpackconfigjs\" aria-label=\"webpackconfigjs permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>webpack.config.js</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">const path = require(&quot;path&quot;);\nconst HtmlWebpackPlugin = require(&quot;html-webpack-plugin&quot;);\nconst { CleanWebpackPlugin } = require(&#39;clean-webpack-plugin&#39;);\nmodule.exports = {\n  mode: &quot;development&quot;,\n  entry: {\n    app: &quot;./src/index&quot;,\n  },\n  resolve: {\n    extensions: [&quot;.ts&quot;, &quot;.js&quot;, &quot;.jsx&quot;]\n  },\n  module: {\n    rules: [\n      {\n        test: /\\.(js|ts)$/,\n        exclude: /node_modules/,\n        use: {\n          loader: &#39;babel-loader&#39;,\n          options: {\n            presets: [\n              &#39;@babel/preset-env&#39;,\n              &#39;@babel/preset-typescript&#39;\n            ],\n            // plugins: [\n            //   &#39;@babel/proposal-class-properties&#39;,\n            //   &#39;@babel/proposal-object-rest-spread&#39;\n            // ]\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  output: {\n    path: path.resolve(__dirname, &quot;dist&quot;),\n    filename: &quot;[name].[hash].js&quot;\n  },\n  devServer: {\n    historyApiFallback: true,\n    open: false,\n    port: 8080,\n    host: &#39;localhost&#39;,\n    hot: true,\n    inline: true\n  },\n  plugins: [\n    new CleanWebpackPlugin(),\n    new HtmlWebpackPlugin({\n      template: `./public/index.html`\n    })\n  ]\n};</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"scss\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#scss\" aria-label=\"scss permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>scss</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add -D css-loader node-sass sass-loader style-loader</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{\n  test: /\\.s[ac]ss$/i,\n  use: [\n    &#39;style-loader&#39;,\n    &#39;css-loader&#39;,\n    &#39;sass-loader&#39;,\n  ]\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p>로더 순서에 따라 에러가 발생한다. 위 순서로 하니 에러가 없다.<br>\n이렇게만 설치해서 사용하면 스타일이 헤더에 추가된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add -D mini-css-extract-plugin</code></pre></div>\n<p>별도의 css파일로 추가되도록 처리해주는 플러그인</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">plugins: [\n    new CleanWebpackPlugin(),\n    new HtmlWebpackPlugin({\n      template: &#39;./public/index.html&#39;\n    }),\n    new MiniCssExtractPlugin({\n      filename: &quot;[name].css&quot;,\n      chunkFilename: &quot;[id].css&quot;\n     })\n  ]</code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/set-typescript-webpack-babel","tagSlugs":["/tag/typescript/","/tag/javascript/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-07-01","description":"프레임워크 없이 typescript, webpack, babel 등 세팅하기","tags":["typescript","javascript"],"title":"Typescript, webpack, babel setting without framework","socialImage":"/bg_work.jpg"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/set-typescript-webpack-babel"}}}